Installation:

	git clone git://github.com/Carmis/vimrc.git ~/.vim

Where possible, Vim plugins are installed as git submodules. Check these out by running the commands:

  cd .vim
  git submodule init
  git submodule update

Create symlinks:

	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Get bash color scheme from https://github.com/gnumoksha/gnome-terminal-colors
Get powerline fonts from https://github.com/powerline/fonts.git
